Acknowledgements:
ISTRICI stands for Structural Inversion of Common Image Gathers, a processing line developed at OGS. 
The version 0 was registered at Societa' Italiana degli Autori ed Editori - SIAE (https://www.siae.it) in 2010.

Umberta Tinivella wrote the beginnings of what is now called ISTRICI package in 2010 
REF: Umberta Tinivella. Software per l'inversione strutturale dai CIG: ISTRICI. Report OGS 2008/73 GDL 19 REDAS.

Then, ISTRICI was expanded and improved in collaboration with Michela Giustiniani.

For further information, please contact: 

Umberta Tinivella (utinivella@ogs.it)
Michela Giustiniani (mgiustiniani@ogs.it)
